headline: CFO: A Timing Methodology Failing For 10 Years
summary: The VictoryShares US 500 Enhanced Volatility Wtd ETF (CFO) combines low-volatility with market timing. It has reduced drawdown and volatility buts result in lower risk-adjusted performance.
